"{\"uid\": \"straitstimes.com-sport-paris-paralympics-the-greatest-ever-say-former-olympics-executives\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Choose edition  Search  singapore  asia  world  opinion  life  business  sport  Visual  Podcasts  SPH Rewards  STClassifieds  Paid press releases  Advertise with us  FAQs  Contact us  Sign up now:Get the biggest sports news in your inbox  Fireworks during the closing ceremony of the Paris 2024 Paralympics Games at the Stade de France Stadium on Sept 8.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 354, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 98, \"end\": 101, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore_Press_Holdings\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.765890154683061e-14, \"text\": \"SPH\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore_Press_Holdings\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore_Press_Holdings\"}, {\"begin\": 147, \"end\": 156, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Advertise_(horse)\", \"score\": 0.9604822703099307, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Advertise\", \"types\": [\"Q7377\", \"Q729\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Advertise_(horse)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Advertise_(horse)\"}, {\"begin\": 239, \"end\": 248, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fireworks\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0531316374350179e-17, \"text\": \"Fireworks\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fireworks\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fireworks\"}, {\"begin\": 284, \"end\": 294, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.479412310285915e-17, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 295, \"end\": 312, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paralympic_Games\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.5123461902521608e-34, \"text\": \"Paralympics Games\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paralympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paralympic_Games\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"PHOTO: EPA-EFE  PublishedSep 09, 2024, 03:26 PM  UpdatedSep 09, 2024, 08:43 PM  PARIS-The Paris Paralympics were the \\\"greatest ever\\\", according to one former  International Olympic Committee (IOC) marketing executive, while another told AFP it \\\"delivered in spades\\\" the thing that people relate most to in sport - emotion.\", \"from\": 356, \"to\": 678, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 446, \"end\": 451, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999781721, \"rank\": 2.1922478260777072e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 515, \"end\": 552, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee (IOC)\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 515, \"end\": 552, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee (IOC)\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mainly packed stadia, iconic venues and the feel-good factor derived from the earlier Olympics turned the Paralympics into a festival of sport, according to Michael Payne, the IOC's former head of marketing.\", \"from\": 680, \"to\": 887, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 837, \"end\": 850, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Payne_(executive)\", \"score\": 0.9998432523751143, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Michael Payne\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Payne_(executive)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Payne_(executive)\"}, {\"begin\": 856, \"end\": 859, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.588676432160742e-25, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Its counterpart, the International Paralympic Committee, can breathe a sigh of relief after Rio de Janeiro was widely criticised for its hosting in 2016 and the Tokyo edition was deprived of spectators because of Covid-19 restrictions.\", \"from\": 889, \"to\": 1124, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 910, \"end\": 944, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Paralympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Paralympic Committee\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Paralympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Paralympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 981, \"end\": 995, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.28263173107108e-15, \"text\": \"Rio de Janeiro\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\"}, {\"begin\": 1050, \"end\": 1055, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.88719332891314e-16, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Paris built on the magic of the Olympic Games and delivered a spectacular Paralympic Games - to my mind the greatest ever,\\\" said Payne.\", \"from\": 1126, \"to\": 1262, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1127, \"end\": 1132, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999781721, \"rank\": 2.1922478260777072e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"All the ingredients that made the Olympics so special have been carried forward to the Paras, delivering an incredible atmosphere.\\\"\", \"from\": 1264, \"to\": 1396, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Another former IOC marketing executive, Terrence Burns, said in his 30-plus years  of Paralympics, there was no comparison \\\"in both fan and commercial interest\\\".\", \"from\": 1398, \"to\": 1559, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1413, \"end\": 1416, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.588676432160742e-25, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"In so many ways, I believe the Paralympics are truly coming into their own as a separate yet complementary 'product' from the Olympics,\\\" Burns said.\", \"from\": 1561, \"to\": 1710, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I give the IOC full marks for working hard to make the Paralympics a product that brands want not only to support, but to market.\", \"from\": 1712, \"to\": 1842, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"(It is) a difference with a profound distinction.\\\"\", \"from\": 1844, \"to\": 1895, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For Payne, who in nearly two decades at the IOC was credited with modernising the organisation's brand and improving its finances through sponsorship, the high profile of the Paralympics had hugely positive ramifications.\", \"from\": 1897, \"to\": 2118, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1941, \"end\": 1944, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.588676432160742e-25, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The Paralympics provides a massive boost worldwide to the disabled movement - bringing the issue of disability front and centre,\\\" said the  Irishman.\", \"from\": 2120, \"to\": 2270, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"(There is) a real legacy from general accessibility to a broader debate and awareness about disability throughout society.\\\"\", \"from\": 2272, \"to\": 2396, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He said that before the Paralympic Games became mainstream, \\\"disability was often hidden and rarely talked about\\\".\", \"from\": 2398, \"to\": 2512, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Payne said the athletes were the main actors in making the Paralympics the spectacle they are, with a knock-on positive impact for disabled people back in their own countries.\", \"from\": 2514, \"to\": 2689, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The stories of what some refer to as 'the super humans' provides an inspirational platform that is impossible to ignore,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 2691, \"to\": 2822, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Everyone recognises the incredible challenges that each Paralympic athlete has had to overcome - and watching their performances in Paris, you look on totally awestruck.\\\"\", \"from\": 2824, \"to\": 2995, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2881, \"end\": 2899, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Para-athletics\", \"score\": 0.9999998355688284, \"rank\": 1.6443114953026426e-07, \"text\": \"Paralympic athlete\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Para-athletics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Para-athletics\"}, {\"begin\": 2957, \"end\": 2962, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999781721, \"rank\": 2.1922478260777072e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Burns also said the athletes drove the narrative.\", \"from\": 2997, \"to\": 3046, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think people react and relate to sport through a single prism: emotion,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 3048, \"to\": 3132, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The Paras deliver on that in spades.\", \"from\": 3134, \"to\": 3171, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3135, \"end\": 3144, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Paras\", \"score\": 0.9999999999395186, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"The Paras\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q15416\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Paras\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Paras\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Increased coverage and exposure means more fans can experience it.\\\"\", \"from\": 3172, \"to\": 3239, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"British amputee sprinter Jonnie Peacock is one who would like that exposure to be even greater.\", \"from\": 3241, \"to\": 3336, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3241, \"end\": 3248, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9998827972515775, \"rank\": 0.00010042174737118117, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 3266, \"end\": 3280, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jonnie_Peacock\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jonnie Peacock\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jonnie_Peacock\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jonnie_Peacock\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The two-time 100m champion made an impassioned plea to World Athletics that Paralympic athletes be included in the main televised section of the elite Diamond League meetings.\", \"from\": 3338, \"to\": 3513, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3393, \"end\": 3408, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 6.683941845259135e-13, \"text\": \"World Athletics\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics\"}, {\"begin\": 3489, \"end\": 3503, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diamond_League\", \"score\": 0.9999747149517891, \"rank\": 2.528484397245789e-05, \"text\": \"Diamond League\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diamond_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diamond_League\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Payne thinks his argument holds water, but says though the Commonwealth Games combine both para and able-bodied events, it would be a no-go for the Olympics to follow suit.\", \"from\": 3515, \"to\": 3687, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3574, \"end\": 3592, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Commonwealth_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999661938912179, \"rank\": 2.6705232755673682e-05, \"text\": \"Commonwealth Games\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Commonwealth_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Commonwealth_Games\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Including Para sports events in individual world championships could well work for certain sports,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 3689, \"to\": 3798, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But a total integration into the Olympics would not work to my mind.\", \"from\": 3800, \"to\": 3869, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Both events are now so big, they each need their own stage... and frankly I think Paralympics are better served on the stage by themselves.\\\"\", \"from\": 3871, \"to\": 4012, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Burns, who since leaving the IOC has assisted five successful Olympic bid city campaigns, says Peacock does have a point.\", \"from\": 4014, \"to\": 4135, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4043, \"end\": 4046, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.588676432160742e-25, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 4109, \"end\": 4116, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peafowl\", \"score\": 0.9999999155825243, \"rank\": 8.440646546852329e-08, \"text\": \"Peacock\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peafowl\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peafowl\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I would also argue that mixing might dilute the focus on Paralympic sport, though (it is) worth experimenting with.\\\"\", \"from\": 4137, \"to\": 4254, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4195, \"end\": 4211, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paralympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 7.625614845896848e-13, \"text\": \"Paralympic sport\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paralympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paralympic_Games\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Burns said the only real downside is the \\\"confusing classifications system\\\".\", \"from\": 4256, \"to\": 4332, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Payne praised the organisation of the Paralympics.\", \"from\": 4334, \"to\": 4384, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He said: \\\"Some joke that the Olympics are just a 'test event' for the real thing, giving the local organisers the time to iron out all the small operational problems!\", \"from\": 4386, \"to\": 4552, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"AFP  Paralympics  Para-athletes  Olympics  France  E-paper  Newsletters  Podcasts  RSS Feed  About Us  Terms & Conditions  Personal Data Protection Notice  Need help?\", \"from\": 4552, \"to\": 4719, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4596, \"end\": 4602, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.9092287832201149, \"rank\": 0.09937885965033574, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\"}, {\"begin\": 4636, \"end\": 4644, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RSS\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"RSS Feed\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RSS\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RSS\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Reach us here.\", \"from\": 4720, \"to\": 4734, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Advertise with us\", \"from\": 4736, \"to\": 4753, \"entities\": []}]}"